msgctxt "#32151"
msgid "Auto: notifications appear on chapter change for the library paths above. Manual: notifications appear only when you press the configured button (works for any media with chapters, not just the library paths). Both: combines Auto and Manual."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "#32152"
msgid "Choose which key summons the chapter notification during fullscreen video. Color buttons (Yellow/Red/Green/Blue) only work on remotes that send those codes (some Logitech Harmony remotes do not). F-keys and letter keys are reliably free in fullscreen video and can be sent by any programmable remote or keyboard. Make sure the chosen key is not already bound by your skin or other addons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "#32153"
msgid "Removes the button binding installed by this addon. Use before uninstalling the addon to avoid leaving an orphaned keymap entry."
msgstr ""

